
		**** Making Movies with Griz ****

Follow is a sequence of steps to generate a movie with Griz:

(1) Select the result variable that you want to plot and the 
    desired view.

(2) Enter the commands:    autoimg FILENAME png
                           on autoimg

(3) Animate the result:    anim

      Look in the current directory where you should see a sequence of
      files such as:
                          FILENAME001.png .... FILENAME9999.png

(4) Make the movie:       convert *.png mymovie.mpg

(5) View the movie:       mplayer (or other movie player) mymovie.mpg
